resources.name: Contactrequeststatus
resources.description:
Only women can change the status of a contact request

IGNORE            = 0;     Man has initiated

ACCEPTED          = 1;     Woman has accepted or initiate the contact request

REFUSED           = 2;     Woman has refused the contact request

SPAM              = 3;     It is spam and must not be shown

EXPIRED           = 4;     The contact request has never been accepted or refused, so it has expired (~30 days)

ACCOUNT_CLOSED    = 5;      The account is closed, in term of process, it is similar with EXPIRED
